{"tid":1183084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請注意！6月9號遊行起點已更改為維園草地","createTime":"2019-06-02T16:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T10:02:28.000Z","uid":205937,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"489d18b9ba668a393cd07a370f69226f02a61b0d","tid":1183084,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:07:39.000Z","msg":"6月9日反「送中」大遊行，最新安排如下：<br />\n<br />\n遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/511608535553209/posts/2281125788601466?s=100001812202118&amp;sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F511608535553209%2Fposts%2F2281125788601466%3Fs%3D100001812202118%26sfns%3Dxmo&d=oOXZKU%2BZRanU2kHQSwewONB4iDtRAy51VXy1YCRVmoY%3D&h=b7ccab0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/511608535553209/posts/2281125788601466?s=100001812202118&amp;sfns=xmo</a>"},{"pid":"57d2406e9704024e3134f58e7e977c241be9e39a","tid":1183084,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:08:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e99e07b71fae815e730a6778afc9381d13a71c58","tid":1183084,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:16:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51acc53af184b7b777506d623291d023ef4b5a60","tid":1183084,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:25:57.000Z","msg":"推，令多啲人知道最新安排，唔會走咗去東角道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaf4058de759d7347764a68bb6c73acc9cbbe0ea","tid":1183084,"uid":94824,"like":2,"dislike":47,"score":-45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:32:28.000Z","msg":"都通過啦遊泥做咩尻"},{"pid":"57e7465132ad45b8f61e169edfe1a0b32e92c44c","tid":1183084,"uid":38666,"like":2,"dislike":29,"score":-27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:37:42.000Z","msg":"入維園等幾個鐘排隊不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食完餐豪華豐富放題再出發都唔遲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港島邊間放題最抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc6b25b732cea91b659afa8dfe4c3ed4b5601488","tid":1183084,"uid":205937,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"eaf4058de759d7347764a68bb6c73acc9cbbe0ea","tid":1183084,"uid":94824,"like":2,"dislike":47,"score":-45,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:32:28.000Z","msg":"都通過啦遊泥做咩尻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:47:24.000Z","msg":"多謝推po"},{"pid":"7cbb4505dd99bc57b4156aa5436c820a4e785569","tid":1183084,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:58:06.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a6d3a70a74b9fa5ce8c6a340b8d7be898ef67d0","tid":1183084,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"1309f77325478f0f5b7e4b296753009a088ca1ee","tid":1183084,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:00:48.000Z","msg":"唔想係維園等咁耐的話<br />\n其實可以遲少少去龍尾加入咪得"},{"pid":"88e7e7666c76031934a18ebefa2e0b4763b4250c","tid":1183084,"uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:02:51.000Z","msg":"參與遊行呼籲：<br />\n<br />\n1. 想與民陣一同起步的遊行參與者，在維園草地集合。<br />\n<br />\n*2. 坐輪椅人士、有需要人士或推嬰兒車的照顧者，可以維園草地旁的「南路」集合，民陣會安排優先出發。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">3. 想中途加入遊行的參與者，可在軒尼斯道西行線（往灣仔方向，於銅鑼灣波斯富街之後的路段加入。但必須在帶頭車及遊行帶頭橫額之後，才加入遊行隊伍。）</span><br />\n<br />\n4. 請所有參與遊行的市民，就長時間遊行做好充足的準備，包括：水、毛巾、手機充電、雨傘、電風扇等等。<br />\n<br />\n無懼政權打壓，6月9日，全港總動員，反「送中」、撤惡法！<br />\n<br />\n民間人權陣線秘書處<br />\n<br />\n#遊行已獲發不反對通知書<br />\n#警方大石壓死蟹<br />\n#警權無限大<br />\n#人權被出賣<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/61620734_2281134285267283_2809325987915890688_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-2.xx&amp;oh=16575c49eeeb52ed852610bdb4b9c290&amp;oe=5D50D13E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F61620734_2281134285267283_2809325987915890688_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-2.xx%26oh%3D16575c49eeeb52ed852610bdb4b9c290%26oe%3D5D50D13E&h=f983196d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e3a20262896e8dec4902561ded1c251482b6bcc","tid":1183084,"uid":89514,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:03:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2092a83ab1e3b1ba21271c427a4aefd2f95d654d","tid":1183084,"uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:06:05.000Z","msg":"好肯定今次會同一時間逼爆維園, 銅鑼灣至金鐘一帶, <br />\n<br />\n延綿唔知幾多個鐘.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d612e3041ac184c3d5cb9cab186439b72f590f5","tid":1183084,"uid":205937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T17:15:01.000Z","msg":"應該重有好多人未知道最新安排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"